Ahead of the forthcoming presidential election, popular Nigerian social activist and skit maker, Debo Adebayo, better known as Mr Macaroni, has called on Nigerians to be more vigilant and vote their conscience. Mr Macaroni’s advice was contained in a post via his verified Twitter handle. He said he would definitely vote for Peter Obi, the Labour Party presidential candidate. He wrote, “I don’t know about you but Peter Obi most definitely has my vote. Dear Nigerians, please open your eyes ooo and vote your conscience. “I am voting mine.”